	- adding ACTION_MORE_CACHE, but reading only...;
	- remove lha-bug (was write error);
	- remove bug in concerning with drawer operation on workbench
	  and assign on cli;
	- bug in documentation in mountlist (some \\ was replaced...)
V0.14   [22.01.1999]
	- try to remove bug with Samba1.9.18p10;
	- adding parameter LOG and PM;
	- reactivate intern log level, only setable with additional
	  prog SetSMBDevLevel;
V0.13   [20.10.1998]
	- printer: if set GFX then /n will no longer expand to /r/n;
	- try to remove bug with Samba1.9.18p10;
V0.12   - try to remove some enforcer-hits while "dir" with Win95 connection;
	- remove bug when the connection not established;
	- some changings in login procedure;
	- add full report for SMB-Net utility;
	- add polish and bugfixed english catalog (thanks to Tomasz Muszynski);
V0.11   - internal;
V0.10   - localisation (buildin english), additional german;
	- remove bug while reconnection;
	- remove enforcer hits read 0;
	- connection will established when mount command finish;
V0.09   - remove bug while workbench create a new subdirectory;
	- remove bug while accessing WinNT shares;
V0.08   - login procedure changed, tested with NT and OS2 (uppercase password),
	  if password wrong/empty ask for it (requiered reqtools.library V38);
	- searching enforcer-hits (read 0) but not realy found;
	- try not to reconnect, if host not found;
	- implement ACTION_FLUSH (was dummy earlier);
	- ixemul is no longer used, bsdsocket call directly;
	- now Manx-C is used;
V0.07   - internal;
V0.06   - login procedure changed '' will replaced to a empty password;
	- program die add to this package;
V0.05   - initial release;


